<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Digital Gloss — Web, Marketing &amp; AI, One Team</title>
<meta name="description" content="Digital Gloss builds sites that load fast, campaigns that convert, and AI tools that do the boring parts for you.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Sans:ital,wght@0,400..700;1,400..700&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="grain"></div>

<header class="nav" id="top">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a class="wordmark" href="#top">Digital<span>Gloss</span></a>
    <nav class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <a href="#services">Services</a>
      <a href="#process">Process</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-small" href="#contact">Get a free quote</a>
    <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Toggle menu" aria-expanded="false">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="top-hero">
    <div class="glow-field" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="glow glow-cyan"></span>
      <span class="glow glow-violet"></span>
      <span class="glow glow-amber"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Web design &amp; development studio, remote-first</p>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">Brands built to<br>outperform, not just exist.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lede">
        Digital Gloss designs and builds the sites, campaigns, and AI-driven
        tools that let ambitious companies run leaner and grow faster —
        work judged by what it does for the business, not how it looks in a deck.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a free quote</a>
        <a href="#services" class="btn btn-ghost">See what we do</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="services" id="services">
    <div class="section-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">What we do</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Three disciplines.<br>One team that ships.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="cards">
      <article class="glass-card" data-shine data-glow="cyan">
        <div class="card-glow"></div>
        <p class="card-tag">Web Development</p>
        <h3>Sites built to sell, not just sit there.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom builds &amp; redesigns</li>
          <li>E-commerce &amp; booking flows</li>
          <li>Speed &amp; SEO baked in from day one</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="glass-card" data-shine data-glow="amber">
        <div class="card-glow"></div>
        <p class="card-tag">Digital Marketing</p>
        <h3>Marketing that earns attention, not just spends budget.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Paid social &amp; search campaigns</li>
          <li>Content &amp; SEO strategy</li>
          <li>Analytics you can actually read</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="glass-card" data-shine data-glow="violet">
        <div class="card-glow"></div>
        <p class="card-tag">AI Solutions</p>
        <h3>AI that does the busywork, so your team doesn't have to.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom chatbots &amp; support tools</li>
          <li>Workflow automation</li>
          <li>Internal tools built around your data</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROCESS -->
  <section class="process" id="process">
    <div class="section-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">How it works</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Four steps.<br>No mystery in between.</h2>
    </div>

    <ol class="process-list">
      <li>
        <span class="process-num">01</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Discovery</h3>
          <p>We dig into your business, your customers, and what's actually broken before we touch a single pixel.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="process-num">02</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Build</h3>
          <p>Design and development happen in the open — you see progress every week, not just at the end.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="process-num">03</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Launch</h3>
          <p>We ship, test against real traffic, and fix what breaks before your customers ever notice.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="process-num">04</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Grow</h3>
          <p>Ongoing marketing and AI tooling keep compounding after launch — growth doesn't stop at go-live.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <!-- STATEMENT -->
  <section class="statement">
    <p class="statement-text">
      Most agencies pick a lane. We figured out the lanes all lead
      to the same place — <em>a brand people actually remember.</em>
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="glow-field" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="glow glow-violet"></span>
      <span class="glow glow-cyan"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Let's talk</p>
      <h2 class="contact-title">Got a project?<br>Let's talk it through.</h2>
      <p class="contact-sub">Tell us what you're building. We'll tell you honestly if we're the right fit.</p>
      <a href="mailto:inquires@digitalgloss.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">inquires@digitalgloss.com</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <a class="wordmark wordmark-small" href="#top">Digital<span>Gloss</span></a>
    <nav class="footer-links">
      <a href="#services">Services</a>
      <a href="#process">Process</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 Digital Gloss. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
